'''The United Arab Emirates''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in June 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Abu Dhabi, along with Dubai.

On June 9, 2019 on [[IOS version|iOS]]; new countries were added. Along with United Arab Emirates; there was also [[Afghanistan]], [[Belgium]], [[Djibouti]], [[Dominican Republic]], [[Iraq]], [[Poland]], [[Puerto Rico]], [[Switzerland]], [[Taiwan]], [[Thailand]], and [[Uruguay]]. It was added to Android September 21, 2019. 

==Information==
Being an Islam-based country, female characters in BitLife will wear hijabs when they are adults. This is shared with females in [[Iran]], [[Iraq]], [[Afghanistan]], or [[Saudi Arabia]].

On IOS, just like in real life, the UAE provides free health care and will provide treatment from medical doctors for no cost or consultation fee.

